Tags:
  - Union-Identity=Realization And Identity=Know Thyself
By: Richard of Saint-Victor
---
The soul which is attempting to rise to the height of knowledge must make
self-knowledge its first and chief concern. The high peak of knowledge is
perfect self-knowledge.
